<div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4">
  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">인근 매각가율 확인</h4>
  <% if region_label.present? %>
    <p data-test="region-label" class="text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-2"><%= region_label %></p>
  <% end %>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-3">
    동 단위 평균 매각가율과 응찰자 수는 법원경매정보 매각결과 검색에서 확인하세요. 본 도구는 입찰가에 따른 비용·세금만 계산합니다.
  </p>
  <a href="<%= NearbyAuctionLinksComponent::COURT_SEARCH_URL %>"
     target="_blank"
     rel="noopener noreferrer"
     class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-200 underline">
    법원경매정보 매각결과 검색 열기
    <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="sr-only">(새 창)</span>
  </a>
</div>
